{
  "page": "On Miasmas",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>On Miasmas</b></i> is an account written by <a href=\"/index.php/Harmon\" title=\"Harmon\">Harmon</a>. It described that animals are more sensitive to polluted waters in <a href=\"/index.php/Asshai\" title=\"Asshai\">Asshai</a>, even without drinking it, causing Asshai to be without horses, elephants, mules, donkeys, <a href=\"/index.php/Zorse\" title=\"Zorse\">zorses</a>, camels and dogs.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_asshai-by-the-shadow.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_asshai-by-the-shadow.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=On_Miasmas&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_asshai-by-the-shadow.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_asshai-by-the-shadow.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Asshai-by-the-Shadow.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404031106\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.021 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.042 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 101/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8555/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 373/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 123/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpe